cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.DC, cs.SI, cs.GT 

This paper discusses the design of an incentive mechanism for a peer-to-peer network, which involves topics related to network infrastructure (cs.NI), multimedia systems (cs.MM), distributed computing (cs.DC), social and information networks (cs.SI), and game theory (cs.GT). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI, followed by cs.MM, cs.DC, cs.SI, and cs.GT.
